[
  {
    "start": 2.48,
    "end": 4,
    "text": "DrJill: Hello, I'm Dr."
  },
  {
    "start": 4,
    "end": 4.72,
    "text": "DrJill: Jill."
  },
  {
    "start": 4.72,
    "end": 8.56,
    "text": "DrJill: Welcome to Let's Learn English with Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 8.56,
    "end": 13.2,
    "text": "DrJill: It is fun to be outdoors and enjoy nature."
  },
  {
    "start": 13.32,
    "end": 18.04,
    "text": "DrJill: Some people go outdoors for many days."
  },
  {
    "start": 18.04,
    "end": 23,
    "text": "DrJill: They do everything outdoors, even sleep."
  },
  {
    "start": 23.88,
    "end": 27.24,
    "text": "DrJill: We call this camping."
  },
  {
    "start": 27.24,
    "end": 31.56,
    "text": "DrJill: Now let's visit Anna's treehouse to learn more."
  },
  {
    "start": 31.56,
    "end": 33.96,
    "text": "DrJill: She answers the question."
  },
  {
    "start": 33.92,
    "end": 36.719,
    "text": "DrJill: What is camping?"
  },
  {
    "start": 39.92,
    "end": 41.44,
    "text": "Anna: Hi, welcome."
  },
  {
    "start": 41.44,
    "end": 42.399,
    "text": "Anna: Hi, Max."
  },
  {
    "start": 42.399,
    "end": 43.6,
    "text": "Anna: Hi, Daisy."
  },
  {
    "start": 43.6,
    "end": 44.559,
    "text": "Max: Hello, Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 44.719,
    "end": 46.559,
    "text": "Anna: What do you see in the back?"
  },
  {
    "start": 46.38,
    "end": 49.34,
    "text": "Anna: This is my camping box."
  },
  {
    "start": 49.34,
    "end": 50.78,
    "text": "Anna: What is that?"
  },
  {
    "start": 50.78,
    "end": 53.34,
    "text": "Anna: A box holds things."
  },
  {
    "start": 53.34,
    "end": 54.7,
    "text": "Anna: B-O-X."
  },
  {
    "start": 54.7,
    "end": 56.14,
    "text": "Anna: It ends in X."
  },
  {
    "start": 56.14,
    "end": 58.38,
    "text": "Anna: X makes the Ks sound"
  },
  {
    "start": 59.02,
    "end": 62.06,
    "text": "Students: I know the word box."
  },
  {
    "start": 62.06,
    "end": 64.78,
    "text": "Students: I mean, what is camping?"
  },
  {
    "start": 64.78,
    "end": 68.14,
    "text": "Max: Anna, I have our question for today."
  },
  {
    "start": 68.14,
    "end": 71.1,
    "text": "Students: Anna, answer my question first."
  },
  {
    "start": 70.64,
    "end": 72.08,
    "text": "Students: What is happening?"
  },
  {
    "start": 72.32,
    "end": 74.24,
    "text": "Max: What me first?"
  },
  {
    "start": 74.24,
    "end": 75.92,
    "text": "Max: The question is helpful."
  },
  {
    "start": 76,
    "end": 79.28,
    "text": "Anna: Daisy, please let me get the question first"
  },
  {
    "start": 82.259,
    "end": 84.34,
    "text": "Anna: What is camping?"
  },
  {
    "start": 84.34,
    "end": 85.78,
    "text": "Anna: Max, you are right."
  },
  {
    "start": 85.78,
    "end": 87.78,
    "text": "Anna: The question is helpful."
  },
  {
    "start": 89.34,
    "end": 95.74,
    "text": "Anna: Camping is playing, eating, and sleeping outdoors."
  },
  {
    "start": 96.22,
    "end": 98.94,
    "text": "Anna: Hey, I have an idea."
  },
  {
    "start": 98.94,
    "end": 100.94,
    "text": "Anna: Let's go camping!"
  },
  {
    "start": 101.259,
    "end": 103.979,
    "text": "Students: No, no, no."
  },
  {
    "start": 104.24,
    "end": 107.28,
    "text": "Students: I do not like the outdoors."
  },
  {
    "start": 107.28,
    "end": 110.56,
    "text": "Students: I am an indoor flower."
  },
  {
    "start": 111.84,
    "end": 115.36,
    "text": "DrJill: You can do many fun things on a camping trip."
  },
  {
    "start": 115.36,
    "end": 117.28,
    "text": "DrJill: You can fish."
  },
  {
    "start": 117.48,
    "end": 120.84,
    "text": "DrJill: Boat, hike, and swim."
  },
  {
    "start": 120.84,
    "end": 126.84,
    "text": "DrJill: You can sit around a campfire and roast marshmallows and sing songs."
  },
  {
    "start": 126.84,
    "end": 129.32,
    "text": "DrJill: Now let's hear from some friends"
  },
  {
    "start": 129.52,
    "end": 133.28,
    "text": "DrJill: They talk about things to do on a camping trip."
  },
  {
    "start": 133.28,
    "end": 134.959,
    "text": "Students: Camping is fun."
  },
  {
    "start": 134.959,
    "end": 137.92,
    "text": "Students: You sleep outside in a tent."
  },
  {
    "start": 137.82,
    "end": 141.58,
    "text": "Students: My favorite part of camping is fishing."
  },
  {
    "start": 141.58,
    "end": 143.26,
    "text": "Students: I love to fish."
  },
  {
    "start": 143.26,
    "end": 147.34,
    "text": "DrJill: On a camping trip, I always bring a sleeping bag."
  },
  {
    "start": 147.32,
    "end": 155.88,
    "text": "DrJill: Camping is fun, but you need special things to go camping, like a tent and sleeping bag."
  },
  {
    "start": 156.44,
    "end": 160.84,
    "text": "DrJill: A list can help you bring all the right things."
  },
  {
    "start": 160.84,
    "end": 165,
    "text": "DrJill: Anna needs to pack her camping things in order."
  },
  {
    "start": 165,
    "end": 167.24,
    "text": "DrJill: So she makes a list."
  },
  {
    "start": 167.68,
    "end": 176.64,
    "text": "DrJill: And she uses helpful numbers like first, second, third, fourth, and more."
  },
  {
    "start": 177.379,
    "end": 180.659,
    "text": "DrJill: Listen for these words."
  },
  {
    "start": 180.659,
    "end": 183.54,
    "text": "Anna: I am going camping."
  },
  {
    "start": 183.54,
    "end": 188.659,
    "text": "Anna: I need to pack my camping things in order."
  },
  {
    "start": 189.18,
    "end": 191.5,
    "text": "Anna: A list helps."
  },
  {
    "start": 192.3,
    "end": 194.06,
    "text": "Anna: Camping things."
  },
  {
    "start": 194.06,
    "end": 197.74,
    "text": "Anna: Please get in my car."
  },
  {
    "start": 197.7,
    "end": 198.98,
    "text": "Anna: In order."
  },
  {
    "start": 201.38,
    "end": 204.26,
    "text": "Anna: First is a tent."
  },
  {
    "start": 206.1,
    "end": 208.9,
    "text": "Anna: Second is a cot"
  },
  {
    "start": 213.02,
    "end": 217.1,
    "text": "Anna: Third is a sleeping bag."
  },
  {
    "start": 219.38,
    "end": 222.26,
    "text": "Anna: Fourth is a grill."
  },
  {
    "start": 225.14,
    "end": 229.38,
    "text": "Anna: Fifth is a flashlight."
  },
  {
    "start": 230.06,
    "end": 231.18,
    "text": "Anna: Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 232.46,
    "end": 235.02,
    "text": "Anna: Thank you, Camping Things."
  },
  {
    "start": 235.02,
    "end": 236.3,
    "text": "Anna: Thank you."
  },
  {
    "start": 239.12,
    "end": 241.28,
    "text": "DrJill: Now let's play a game."
  },
  {
    "start": 241.28,
    "end": 244.96,
    "text": "DrJill: Here are five things Anna needs for camping."
  },
  {
    "start": 247.78,
    "end": 249.78,
    "text": "Students: Which thing is third?"
  },
  {
    "start": 249.78,
    "end": 255.14,
    "text": "Anna: The sleeping bag is third on the list."
  },
  {
    "start": 255.14,
    "end": 256.82,
    "text": "Students: Which thing?"
  },
  {
    "start": 256.82,
    "end": 258.18,
    "text": "Students: is fifth."
  },
  {
    "start": 258.18,
    "end": 262.74,
    "text": "Anna: The flashlight is fifth on the list."
  },
  {
    "start": 263.06,
    "end": 266.1,
    "text": "Students: Which thing is first?"
  },
  {
    "start": 266.1,
    "end": 271.22,
    "text": "Anna: The tent is first on the list."
  },
  {
    "start": 270.16,
    "end": 271.12,
    "text": "DrJill: Great job!"
  },
  {
    "start": 271.36,
    "end": 277.44,
    "text": "DrJill: Use words like first, second, and third to tell the order of things."
  },
  {
    "start": 277.44,
    "end": 282.16,
    "text": "DrJill: And you can talk about camping in English with your friends and family"
  },
  {
    "start": 282.96,
    "end": 288,
    "text": "DrJill: Join us again next time on Let's Learn English with Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 288,
    "end": 293.52,
    "text": "Students: Take me home, country road."
  }
]
